        "Title": "Pour One Out",
        "Description": "Good Evening, Agent. Your target is the Club Crew security team at the Holle Club. Eliminate them discreetly to send a message to their corrupt employer, Rolf. Precision and subtlety are key--ensure no civilian casualties and maintain your cover. The stage is set, good hunting.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as GlitchFood.",
